4 main ways to expres position

sticky: can be positioned anywhere however when scrolling down, 
    the "sticky" element will stick to the top search bar

relative: position is with respect to the previous element
    -generally used for child elements to reference off of for position

absolute: position is with respect to the previous relative element

fixed: fixed relative to the current screen, not the html element

*typing height: #vh will allow you to scroll if the number is big enough
